T*
(is what gives the paragraph depth. However, the reflection currently exists at a conceptual) Tj
T*
(level. To elevate it further, the writer should include a specific detail from the moment) Tj
T*
(being reflected on. At elite level, reflection becomes strongest when abstract insight is) Tj
T*
(anchored in something concrete. The thinking is already strong; the next step is grounding) Tj
