() Tj
T*
(This paragraph is effective because it introduces resistance, which is essential in) Tj
T*
(reflective writing. Growth only feels meaningful when there is something to resist or) Tj
T*
(misunderstand. The writer shows that they did not immediately accept the significance of the) Tj
T*
(moment, which makes the reflection more believable. The tension between dismissal and) Tj
T*
(persistence is particularly strong. To elevate this further, the writer should explore why) Tj
T*
(the moment was dismissed. Understanding that resistance adds depth and complexity to the) Tj
T*
(reflection.) Tj
